<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The following application config will not work as expected</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$config = array(
    'autoloaderprefixes' =&gt; array(
        'My' =&gt; 'path/to/My'
    ),
);
$app = new Zend\Application($config);
</code></pre>

<p>Because {{autoloaderprefixes}} config option is omited by {{Zend\Application}} during construction.</p>

